					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This one didn't make sense to me at first, but I do like it. It's weird enough to be an SCP, but not super creepy.</p> <p>I like creepy sometimes, but this also kind of warmed my heart a bit. Some people, however magical, still clinging to the old ways.</p> <p>+1'd. Looking forward to future stuff from you.</p> 
				 	]]>
