					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is my first SCP, based in the history of my local area. I'd really like to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oz-ouroboros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1743859&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1493074839" alt="OZ Ouroboros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1743859)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oz-ouroboros" >OZ Ouroboros</a></span>, kenneth &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/subtletea" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2936027&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1493074839" alt="subtletea" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2936027)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/subtletea" >subtletea</a></span> in chat for all their help, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2039383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1493074839" alt="MrWrong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2039383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrwrong" >MrWrong</a></span> in the forums for helping me pare it down to something with pace.</p> <p>The image comes from the wikipedia article on fen-skating and is in the public domain. Let me know if I need to attribute more thoroughly or add anything else.</p> 
				 	]]>
